    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in a few areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and a few stains on the carpet. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind doing a little bit of cosmetic or preventative maintenance.",
