    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and still looks great hitting the road! It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for plenty more adventures with its next owner. If you're looking for a solid, comfy car that won't let you down, this is definitely the one for you. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 28900.0,
