      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained car that looks and drives beautifully. The exterior paint retains a deep shine, showing only the minor, superficial character marks typical of a cared-for vehicle of its age. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the seats are supportive with minimal wear, and all interior features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a smooth-shifting transmission and an engine that starts eagerly and runs quietly. We have recently completed a full fluid flush and a comprehensive safety inspection to ensure it is road-trip ready. This is a solid, honest car that offers a premium driving experience and many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
